<% content_for :title, "About PR!OR!TY!" %>

<div class="max-w-lg mx-auto space-y-8 py-4">

  <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-center">
    About PR<span class="text-brand-blue">!</span>OR<span class="text-brand-green">!</span>TY<span class="text-brand-red">!</span>
  </h1>

  <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
    <p>
      PR!OR!TY! is a simple task management app built around one idea: <span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">get everything out of your head, then focus on what matters most.</span>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-text-primary pt-2">How it works</h2>

    <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3">
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Brain dump.</span>
        Write down everything you can think of. Every task, errand, idea, and thing you've been meaning to do. Don't worry about order or importance yet — just get it all out of your head and into a list.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Sort by priority.</span>
        Drag and drop your tasks into order. Put the most important things at the top. This is where you decide what actually matters right now.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Enter focus mode.</span>
        Switch to the Focus tab and all the noise disappears. You're left with just your top priority tasks — no distractions, no endless list to scroll through. Complete what's in front of you, and the next task rises to the top.
      </li>
    </ol>

    <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-bold text-text-primary pt-2">Features</h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
      <li><span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Multiple lists</span> — organise different areas of your life separately.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Categories</span> — tag tasks with colour-coded categories to filter your view.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Snooze</span> — hide tasks until a specific date so they're not cluttering your list.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Shared lists</span> — invite others by email and collaborate in real time.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Configurable focus</span> — choose how many tasks appear in focus mode per list.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="pt-2">
      The goal is simple: stop thinking about everything at once, and start doing the one thing that matters most.
    </p>

  </div>

  <p class="text-center text-sm text-text-tertiary">
    PR!OR!TY! was made by <%= link_to "DAZ", "https://daz.codes", target: "_blank", class: "font-semibold text-text-secondary hover:text-text-primary no-underline" %>.
  </p>

  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <%= link_to "Back", root_path, class: "text-sm text-text-tertiary hover:text-text-secondary no-underline" %>
  </div>

</div>
